title: ITT: We list things about League that would've seemed crazy one year ago
body:
[Last year's thread](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/GD/Ly2a5qme-itt-we-list-things-about-league-that-wouldve-seemed-crazy-6-months-ago)

One year ago, the Taric rework was about to go live. Aurelion Sol had come out a couple weeks ago and in about a month Taliyah would be released.
